item.description: Throughout his career, he has built a number of large-scale, cross-country OSS/BSS platforms/systems and operation tools, most of them are still running in productions. He loves open source and has been contributing to a variety of open source projects, including Istio(Service Mesh https://istio.io), ONAP(Open Network Automation Platform https://wiki.onap.org), Hugo(static site generators https://themes.gohugo.io/hugo-theme-cleanwhite/), etc. He also has strong interests in various tech stuff such as Artificial Intelligence, Cryptocurrencies, Smart Home.
